category: Devel
requires: libctpl2 libglib2.0-devel
external-source: ctpl
sdesc: "C Template Parser Library (development)"
ldesc: "CTPL is a template library written in C. It allows fast and easy 
parsing of templates from many sources (including in-memory data and 
local and remote streaming, thanks to GIO) and fine control over 
template parsing environment."
